  "slug": "compressed-box",
  "title": "Compressed Box",
  "description": "Create Compressed Boxes to gain space in your base",
  "body": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><img src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/compressed_box\" width=\"308\" height=\"307\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://discord.gg/nFBAXfb\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Discord&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=5865f2&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"117\" height=\"28\"></a><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://github.com/iglee42\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=GitHub&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=000000&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"108\" height=\"28\"></a><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@iglee42\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=YouTube&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=FF0000&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"118\" height=\"28\"></a><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/iglee42/projects\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=CurseForge&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=f16436&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"143\" height=\"28\"></a><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/iglee42\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Modrinth&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=1ace65&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"129\" height=\"28\"></a></div>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/compressed/overview\" width=\"832\" height=\"208\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #808080; font-size: 30px;\">Welcome to Compressed Box.</span><span style=\"color: #f90;\">&nbsp;</span><br></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">This mod adds Compressed boxes <img src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/compressed/box\" alt=\"\" width=\"39\" height=\"39\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">These boxes helps you to optimise your base by creating spaces where you can build everything you want.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">The mod was inspired by the mods <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/compact-machines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Compact Machines</a> and <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/hyperbox target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Hyperbox</a></span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/compressed/features\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\"></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 28px;\">Chunk Loaders</span></strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/compressed/chunkloader\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"159\"> <img src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/compressed/infinite_loader\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"159\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">The chunk loader is used to keep things loaded in your whole box.<br>It need to be charged with glowstone in order to work correctly.<br><br>Its variant, the infinite chunk loader don't need to be charged with glowstone.<br>It will always load your box.<br>To create it, just use a regular chunk loader on a beacon.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 28px;\">Slots</span></strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/compressed/slot\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"159\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">The slot is used to store items inside of you box.<br>You can insert items to it directly with hopper and pipes.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><br>The block linked to your box can also be used as an interface for all the slots in it.<br>It means that if try to insert items from the box block, it will automatically store them into the slots inside the box.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 28px;\">Tanks</span></strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/compressed/tank\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"159\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">The tank is a slot but for fluids.<br>You can insert fluids to it directly with pipes or by right clicking it with buckets.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><br>Like slots, the block linked to your box can also be used as an interface for all the tanks in it.<br>It means that if try to insert fluids from the box block, it will automatically store them into the tanks inside the box.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 28px;\">The Action Bar</span></strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/compressed/actionbar\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"81\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">The action bar is a feature that can be activated in the box .<br>It can be shown by pressed the associated keybind (default : Left Alt).<br>To activate an action from the bar just use the 'Place Block' keybind (default : Right Click)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><br>The different actions from the bar are respectively :</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Set Entry Point</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Rename Box</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Leave Box</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Export Box as Schematic</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Configure Client Settings</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Help with the mod</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/compressed/informations\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">You can use the mod on your modpack , but you can't repost the mod on an another website !</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Curseforge and Modrinth are the only websites where the mod was posted</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><a href=\"https://billing.sparkedhost.com/aff.php?aff=2723\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/829380/description_351e5b5a-1c0d-493f-bb82-932420236878.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"133\"></a></p>\n</div>",
